-- Knicks Beat Portland in First Game After Coach D’Antoni Leaves
-- B y   R o b   G l o s t e r
-- 2012-03-15T02:04:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-15/knicks-beat-portland-in-first-game-after-coach-d-antoni-leaves.html
The  New York Knicks  beat the
Portland Trail Blazers 121-79 hours after  Mike D’Antoni  left the
team as coach.  The win at Madison Square Garden in  New York  ended a six-
game losing streak for the Knicks.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Larry Siddons at 
 lsiddons@bloomberg.net  